    <div class="container">
        <div class="clue-box" id="clueBox">
            
            <!-- LOCKED STATE -->
            <div class="locked-content">
                <div class="clue-title">Records Investigation</div>
                <div class="clue-subtitle">This requires investigative expertise</div>
                
                <div class="password-group">
                    <input type="password" id="passwordInput" class="password-input" placeholder="Enter Password">
                    <button onclick="checkPassword()" class="submit-btn">Investigate</button>
                </div>
                <div class="error-msg" id="errorMsg">Incorrect password. Find someone with investigative skills.</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- UNLOCKED STATE -->
            <div class="unlocked-content">
                <div class="skill-badge">Background Investigation</div>
                <div class="reveal-header">Subject: Miranda Longfellow</div>
                <div class="reveal-content">
                    <p>A background investigation into Miranda Longfellow has revealed a significant discrepancy:</p>
                    
                    <div class="reveal-danger">
                        "There is no record of a 'Miranda Longfellow' existing prior to 1920. No birth certificate, no school records, no employment history. The identity appears to have been created."
                    </div>
                    
                    <p>Further investigation into similar records revealed a match:</p>
                    
                    <div class="reveal-highlight">
                        "A 'Miranda Hartley' was born June 3, 1896, in Dallas, Texas. Father: Robert Hartley. Mother: Margaret Hartley."
                    </div>
                    
                    <p>Miranda Longfellow <strong>is</strong> Miranda Hartley — the daughter of Robert Hartley, William Thoreson's former business partner.</p>
                    
                    <p>She changed her name and has been working as Scott Thoreson's legal assistant for nearly ten years — right under the family's nose.</p>
                    
                    <div class="reveal-danger">
                        "Miranda Hartley is the daughter of the man whose company was stolen. She has been hiding in plain sight."
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // TEST PASSWORD - change later
        const CORRECT_PASSWORD = "open";
        
        function checkPassword() {
            const input = document.getElementById('passwordInput');
            const error = document.getElementById('errorMsg');
            const box = document.getElementById('clueBox');
            
            if (input.value.toLowerCase() === CORRECT_PASSWORD.toLowerCase()) {
                box.classList.add('unlocked');
            } else {
                error.style.display = 'block';
                input.value = '';
            }
        }
        
        // Allow Enter key
        document.getElementById('passwordInput').addEventListener('keypress', function(e) {
            if (e.key === 'Enter') {
                checkPassword();
            }
        });
    </script>
